<p>Identification of item, date; Bernard Berg Collection; RG 065; box number; folder number or item identifier; Poly Archives at Bern Dibner Library of Science and Technology, New York University.</p>  </prefercite>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_98ed050cbf81dc42bf47b2ec308b1e42">
    <head>Scope and Contents</head>
<p>This collection contains sections of the Apollo Operations Handbook and one original lab notebook (computation notebook) from Polytech alum, Bernard Berg.</p>  </scopecontent>
